    <item>
      <title>能源股发行量不足使卡尔加里银行家面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/dearth-of-canadian-energy-financings-leads-to-banker-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大股市除石油和天然气公司外，股票发行均出现反弹，石油和天然气公司的股票发行已枯竭，投资银行正在缩减其在卡尔加里的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/dearth-of-canadian-energy-financings-leads-to-banker-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:13:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>KKR 称投资者“过于关注”信用利差</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/kkr-says-investors-are-too-focused-on-credit-spreads-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR 合伙人兼信贷市场联席主管克里斯·谢尔顿 (Chris Sheldon) 表示：“我们现在看好信贷，我们认为利率处于较高的静息心率水平”，因为他的公司认为投资者错过了信用评级较低且划算的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-17/kkr-says-investors-are-too-focused-on-credit-spreads-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:59:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
